00:16:32.700 --> 00:16:35.869 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
大体 お前
俺を見て怖くないのか

282
00:16:36.203 --> 00:16:40.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
俺はトナカイなのに
二本足で立ってるし しゃべるし

283
00:16:40.791 --> 00:16:44.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
ウフッ 何
あんた 私を怖がらせたいわけ？

284
00:16:47.256 --> 00:16:48.590 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（チョッパー）青っ鼻だし

285
00:16:58.934 --> 00:17:00.769 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（ルフィ）
そこにいたか トナカイ

286
00:17:00.894 --> 00:17:02.646 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ギャーッ

287
00:17:03.355 --> 00:17:05.691 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（ルフィ･サンジ）待てーっ

288
00:17:06.316 --> 00:17:07.651 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
あ…

289
00:17:09.194 --> 00:17:11.488 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（くれは）
フッ すばしっこいガキどもだ

290
00:17:14.616 --> 00:17:16.660 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
感心しないね 小娘

291
00:17:16.785 --> 00:17:17.703 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（ナミ）えっ？

292
00:17:17.828 --> 00:17:21.457 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
（くれは）
私のいない間に
許可なくトナカイを誘惑かい

293
00:17:21.582 --> 00:17:24.793 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
あら 男を口説くのに
許可が必要なの？

294
00:17:24.918 --> 00:17:26.545 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（くれは）
ヒーッヒヒヒヒッ…

295
00:17:26.670 --> 00:17:28.130 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
いや 要らないさ

296
00:17:28.255 --> 00:17:30.215 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
持っていきたきゃ
持っていきな

297
00:17:30.340 --> 00:17:32.968 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
だがね 一筋縄じゃいかないよ

298
00:17:33.260 --> 00:17:35.304 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
あいつは 心に傷を持ってる

299
00:17:35.429 --> 00:17:38.182 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
私でも治せない 大きな傷さ

300
00:17:38.307 --> 00:17:42.269 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
この世に生まれた瞬間に
群れと親にも見放された

301
00:17:42.394 --> 00:17:43.270 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
えっ…

302
00:17:44.396 --> 00:17:46.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（くれは）
青っ鼻だったからさ

303
00:17:47.066 --> 00:17:49.276 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
あいつは いつでも
群れの最後を―

304
00:17:49.401 --> 00:17:51.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
１人寂しく 離れて歩いた

305
00:17:51.904 --> 00:17:54.281 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
生まれたての子供がだよ

306
00:17:54.490 --> 00:17:57.618 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
そして ある日
“悪魔の実”を食っちまって―

307
00:17:57.743 --> 00:18:00.287 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
やつは いよいよ化け物扱い

308
00:18:12.758 --> 00:18:16.011 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
（くれは）
トナカイたちは
あいつを激しく追い立てた

309
00:18:16.261 --> 00:18:20.182 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
もう完全に 普通の
トナカイじゃなくなってたのさ

310
00:18:21.350 --> 00:18:24.353 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
それでも
仲間が欲しかったんだね

311
00:18:24.478 --> 00:18:27.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
今度は 人として 人里に下りた

312
00:18:28.148 --> 00:18:30.567 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（村人）
おい　何だ あの生き物は

313
00:18:30.692 --> 00:18:34.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
（くれは）
だが その姿も
まだ 完全な人形(ひとがた)じゃない

314
00:18:34.947 --> 00:18:37.366 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
どういうわけか
青っ鼻も変わらない

315
00:18:37.491 --> 00:18:38.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（村人たち）キャーッ

316
00:18:38.325 --> 00:18:39.535 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（村人Ａ）来た 雪男だ

317
00:18:39.660 --> 00:18:42.830 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
（村人Ｂ）
危ないぞ
子供たちを早く うちの中へ

318
00:18:44.456 --> 00:18:45.999 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（村人Ｃ）
銃だ 銃を持ってこい

319
00:18:46.125 --> 00:18:47.084 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（村人Ｄ）撃ち殺せ

320
00:18:47.209 --> 00:18:48.502 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（村人Ｅ）化け物め

321
00:18:48.627 --> 00:18:50.170 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（村人Ｆ）向こうへ行け

322
00:18:51.088 --> 00:18:52.589 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（石が当たる音）

323
00:18:52.714 --> 00:18:53.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（銃声）

324
00:19:05.811 --> 00:19:07.146 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（村人）撃ち殺せ

325
00:19:09.815 --> 00:19:12.401 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（くれは）
何が悪いのか分からない

326
00:19:12.526 --> 00:19:15.571 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
何を恨めばいいのかも
分からない

327
00:19:15.696 --> 00:19:17.364 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（村人）この化け物

328
00:19:17.489 --> 00:19:19.533 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（こだまする声）この化け物…

329
00:19:19.658 --> 00:19:22.119 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
（くれは）
ただ 仲間が
欲しかっただけなのに

330
00:19:22.244 --> 00:19:24.037 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
化け物と呼ばれる

331
00:19:24.454 --> 00:19:28.542 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
もう トナカイでもない
人間でもない

332
00:19:30.335 --> 00:19:34.798 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
あいつはね そうやって
１人で生きてきたんだ

333
00:19:35.799 --> 00:19:39.469 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
お前たちに
あいつの心を癒やせるかい

334
00:19:41.763 --> 00:19:46.059 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
（サンジ）
おい ルフィ 見ろよ
あの扉 正面入り口 全開だぜ

335
00:19:46.185 --> 00:19:47.019 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（ルフィ）あ？

336
00:19:49.813 --> 00:19:52.649 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ううっ 寒(さみ)いわけだよ

337
00:19:52.774 --> 00:19:54.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（サンジ）
とにかくこの扉 閉めよう

338
00:19:54.735 --> 00:19:57.446 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
これじゃあ 城の中も外も
変わんねえよ

339
00:19:57.821 --> 00:20:00.782 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
（チョッパー）
おい やめろ
その扉に触るな

340
00:20:01.325 --> 00:20:02.284 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（２人）あ？

341
00:20:03.410 --> 00:20:06.330 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
構うな 閉めよう
こっちが凍っちまうぜ

342
00:20:06.455 --> 00:20:07.247 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（ルフィ）そりゃそうだ

343
00:20:07.664 --> 00:20:10.209 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
おい やめろって
言ってんのが―

344
00:20:10.667 --> 00:20:12.669 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
分かんねえのかーっ！

345
00:20:13.253 --> 00:20:15.339 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ああ ああ

346
00:20:16.173 --> 00:20:17.216 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
うーっ

347
00:20:17.341 --> 00:20:20.594 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
何だよ 何だよ
何怒ってんだ あいつ

348
00:20:22.512 --> 00:20:25.015 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（サンジ）
おい ルフィ 来てみろ こっち

349
00:20:25.974 --> 00:20:26.975 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（ルフィ）あん？

350
00:20:29.228 --> 00:20:30.646 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（サンジ）フーッ

351
00:20:31.939 --> 00:20:33.065 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
上 見てみな

352
00:20:33.565 --> 00:20:34.691 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
うん？

353
00:20:35.067 --> 00:20:35.943 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
あっ

354
00:20:39.112 --> 00:20:41.490 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（鳥の鳴き声）

355
00:20:41.865 --> 00:20:45.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
スノーバードのヒナだ
まあ 扉閉めりゃ落ちるわな

356
00:20:46.411 --> 00:20:48.914 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（ルフィ）
それで閉めらんねえのか

357
00:20:59.299 --> 00:21:02.052 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（２人）うあっ 寒っ

358
00:21:04.304 --> 00:21:05.555 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
待てよ

359
00:21:05.681 --> 00:21:06.848 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
何だ
（ルフィ）わーっ

360
00:21:07.474 --> 00:21:09.685 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
あいつ さっき
しゃべってなかったか

361
00:21:10.227 --> 00:21:12.771 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
そういや あいつ
二本足で立ってたような

362
00:21:14.940 --> 00:21:16.942 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（２人）バケモンだ！

363
00:21:17.985 --> 00:21:20.904 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（ルフィ）
あ… なっ 何だ ありゃ

364
00:21:21.488 --> 00:21:23.448 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
二本足で歩いて

365
00:21:23.573 --> 00:21:24.408 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（サンジ）トナカイで

366
00:21:24.533 --> 00:21:26.076 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（ルフィ）モコモコで
（サンジ）チビで

367
00:21:26.201 --> 00:21:27.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（ルフィ）でかくなって

368
00:21:28.245 --> 00:21:30.205 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（２人）バケモンで…

369
00:21:44.678 --> 00:21:47.306 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（ルフィ）
…いいやつだ　面白(おもしれ)え

370
00:21:47.556 --> 00:21:51.476 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
サンジ あいつ 仲間にしよう！

371
00:21:54.604 --> 00:22:00.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
♪～

372
00:22:59.377 --> 00:23:05.383 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
